      <title>美国银行称投资者对长期美国债券的兴趣正在飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/bofa-says-investor-appetite-for-longer-dated-us-bonds-is-surging</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行的一项客户调查显示，自美联储暗示不太可能加息以来，对长期美国债券的兴趣激增，为今年晚些时候的降息奠定了基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/bofa-says-investor-appetite-for-longer-dated-us-bonds-is-surging</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 13:00:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
