      <title>Sweetgreen 上调 2024 年销售前景后股价大幅上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/sweetgreen-boosts-2024-outlook-as-pricier-salads-fuel-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Sweetgreen Inc. 的股价周五大幅上涨，此前这家沙拉连锁店提高了年度销售预期，并在寻求扩大业务的同时提高了盈利能力。]]></description>
